_sText: This is a glass map with walls and walls! Lots of glass and lots of places to hide and explore. Solid floor spawning points so the noobs cant TK ya! Nice far drop with a toxic pool included for floating corpse goodness! Plenty of room for all stratigies, whether you're a camper,sniper,nader, or whatever you like, there's plenty to do here! enjoy, glass fiends!
